Purpose:
The purpose of this project is to create a virtual robot which answers any question related to IIIT Naya Raipur without the intervention of man-kind.


Aim:
The aim of the project is described below:
To create a conversational agent which can respond to queries related to IIIT Naya Raipur.
To use the techniques of Natural Language Processing to identify the keywords and match them in the defined database.
To use the defined libraries to perform Text to Speech and vice-versa processing.
To make the robot understand the usage of multiple Keywords.
To use the defined libraries to perform the identification of the required web pages.
To design a web-based user interface. 
